data.description: Rare and outstanding single level traditional with 3 car garage on fully fenced lot with ADA master bathroom w/outside entrance through covered patio into master bedroom. Seller has made many updates recently including new roof, interior paint and trim, switches, light fixtures, new butcher block kitchen counters, extensive laminate flooring, painted kitchen cabinets, barn door slider into utility and more. Play structure included...Even has RV parking! Situated in quiet neighborhood on edge of town..close to parks and schools!
